[{"id":"c2746d8c-a90a-4fd4-89e2-1a4ff55c1614","type":"heading","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":1,"isToggleable":false},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"File Overview: ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"jarvis.py","styles":{"code":true}}],"children":[]},{"id":"894a25ab-52ec-418a-a215-5d7434e8bd76","type":"paragraph","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"jarvis.py","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" module serves as the central orchestration hub for the entire Jarvis analysis framework. It defines the ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"CallGraphGenerator","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" class, which acts as the "brain" of the system, coordinating the various subsystems located in the ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"machinery","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" folder to produce a comprehensive model of a Python project.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"16a2ac03-929f-4e13-800f-20f629f503ed","type":"paragraph","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"This file is responsible for managing the lifecycle of an analysis session—from environment setup and dependency hooking to the final extraction of graph edges, class hierarchies, and module metadata.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"3da542e6-db07-40f5-b503-9ae74b5d64b6","type":"divider","props":{},"children":[]},{"id":"a496dace-26ab-4317-acad-0b47a83a0ce6","type":"heading","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":3,"isToggleable":false},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Core Purpose and Role","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"07f25213-b432-479d-9fe9-c405e051cbd8","type":"paragraph","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The primary goal of this module is to integrate disparate analysis components into a unified workflow:","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"27ce29aa-82e2-482d-8e45-a7a86e94ed95","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"System Orchestration","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":": It initializes and holds references to the ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"ScopeManager","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":", ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"DefinitionManager","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":", ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"ImportManager","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":", ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"ClassManager","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":", ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"ModuleManager","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":", and others, ensuring they share a consistent state.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"a7f61208-3250-4d88-ac0c-a5bc7b383424","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Analysis Lifecycle","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":": It manages the execution of analysis "passes" via the ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"do_pass","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" method, which utilizes processors (like ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"ExtProcessor","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":") to traverse the source code.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"c0330cc8-74a5-48e1-9ef3-f91c9708b368","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Environment Management","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":": It configures global settings (such as precision levels via ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"gol","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":") and manages Python's import system hooks to track dependencies in real-time.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"b2765d5c-b1e2-495d-843d-14b598e50b57","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Data Extraction","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":": It provides a high-level API for retrieving the results of the analysis, including the final call graph edges, internal/external module lists, and Method Resolution Orders (MRO) for classes.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"c05324db-5f91-4f6f-8e40-01c64fa854a1","type":"divider","props":{},"children":[]},{"id":"69bbdd97-9ec0-48ea-90e6-9807b6b33840","type":"heading","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":3,"isToggleable":false},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Components","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"e403f9b3-7999-421c-a0b1-01416b3ef93d","type":"heading","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":4,"isToggleable":false},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"CallGraphGenerator","styles":{"code":true}}],"children":[]},{"id":"65e85f8f-fd07-43a0-a140-d41238aa8433","type":"paragraph","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The flagship class of the framework. It encapsulates the entire state of an analysis run.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"81ec9f81-705d-400f-8e47-c188b019c3cf","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"setUp()","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":": Prepares the internal machinery, initializes global registries, and configures precision modes.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"34334b42-11cb-4478-854b-21bc0d707f52","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"do_pass()","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":": The execution engine that iterates through entry points, installs import hooks, and invokes the AST processors to build the model.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"67c67f4b-739d-487a-b04f-2e7a00aefa5d","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Result Exporters","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":": Methods like ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"output_edges()","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":", ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"output_internal_mods()","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":", and ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"output_classes()","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" transform complex internal objects into structured data suitable for formatting and reporting.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"ab0a647a-420f-40ed-8199-522f243e2574","type":"divider","props":{},"children":[]},{"id":"726c8735-a5ed-4c58-9473-2be7a8143ea1","type":"heading","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":3,"isToggleable":false},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"System Integration & Relationship","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"b8fe6831-9480-46e3-8d7d-934321e3f8cf","type":"paragraph","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"jarvis.py","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" sits between the user interface and the low-level logic:","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"2dcad99e-7067-4a19-baee-2513308e989e","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Upstream","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":": It is invoked by ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"jarvis_cli.py","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":", which passes user configuration (like the package path and precision toggle) to the generator.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"d7951918-02b1-47a5-821e-93e21f8bd12d","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Downstream","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":": It drives the ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"machinery","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" modules. It creates the managers that the ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"ExtProcessor","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" uses to record findings during its traversal of the Abstract Syntax Tree.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"ad87b0a7-9954-4f3d-948f-a1087518d87c","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Global State","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":": It initializes the ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"gol","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" (Global Object List) utility, ensuring that settings like ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"precision","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" are visible to deep-level components like the ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"Definition","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" class.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"d2f65fe6-b8a4-452a-b976-b166771f87fe","type":"divider","props":{},"children":[]},{"id":"af23a57e-0a34-4baa-9321-24b17de2fe6e","type":"heading","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":3,"isToggleable":false},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Brief Insight / Tutorial","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"55ab0c0e-bb5e-40b6-8377-9f6f38067793","type":"heading","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":4,"isToggleable":false},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Running an Analysis","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"1a84dd5b-2039-44c3-bca6-022f2e941a36","type":"paragraph","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"CallGraphGenerator","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" is designed to be highly configurable. To analyze a project programmatically:","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"4069757c-d59e-4b0a-9866-f5ffa0ca1ea3","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Initialization","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":":","styles":{}}],"children":[{"id":"f9ebefe3-f837-4e35-9711-040109b6f4b9","type":"codeBlock","props":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"generator = CallGraphGenerator(
    entry_points=["main.py"], 
    package="/path/to/project", 
    precision=True
)","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"90daeb52-aa7c-4e47-a0be-acd0ac9a384d","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Execution","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":": Calling ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"generator.analyze()","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" triggers the ","styles":{}},{"type":"text","text":"do_pass","styles":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" logic, which walks through the code and populates all internal managers.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"020ac557-dd60-46c4-a90e-826e6df1269d","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Consumption","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":":","styles":{}}],"children":[{"id":"f5d8e68a-8b50-40e0-82f5-16da47de0ebd","type":"codeBlock","props":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"edges = generator.output_edges()
for src, dest in edges:
    print(f"Call detected: {src} -> {dest}")","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"43c9150c-c0a4-40b8-b2b4-b4199f065419","type":"paragraph","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"This centralized approach ensures that while the analysis logic is complex and multi-faceted, the interface for executing and retrieving results remains clean and consistent.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"05e34bec-784f-42e2-9e36-4ff699b96a68","type":"paragraph","props":{"backgroundColor":"default","textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[],"children":[]}]
